  "title": "HR Recruiter",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle full cycle of recruitment from screening and shortlisting, to interviewing potential job seekers, to coordinating of interviews, and administering of appointment letters.</li>\n  <li>Partner closely with established Clients to provide expert advice on recruitment strategies and market insights.</li>\n  <li>Handle onboarding and offboarding of contract staff.</li>\n  <li>Drive business growth by networking and engaging with Hiring Managers.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's Degree in any discipline.</li>\n  <li>No prior experience required as full training and support will be provided.</li>\n  <li>Possess high energy and must be a team player.</li>\n  <li>Resourceful and results oriented.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Pls email your detailed resume to aaronteo@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Aaron Teo Yiau Bing (CEI No. R1103712)<br>\nRecruit Express Pte Ltd<br>\nEA Licence No. 99C4599</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
